<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.2">
<l>nāṇi yiṉiyōr karumamillai nālaya lāru maṟintoḻintār</l>
<l>pāṇiyā teṉṉai maruntuceytu paṇṭupaṇ ṭākka vuṟutirākil</l>
<l>māṇi yuruvā yulakaḷanta māyaṉaik kāṇiṟ ṟalaimaṟiyu</l>
<l>māṇaiyāl nīreṉṉaik kākkavēṇṭi lāyppāṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing to be done now by being ashamed:</l>
<l rend="indent">even a few outsiders have come to know [of it]!</l>
<l>Remedying [this] without delaying,</l>
<l rend="indent">if you are thinking of turning me like before,</l>
<l rend="indent">if you truly seek to protect me,</l>
<l>send me to Gokula, where [this] disease will disappear if [I] see the Marvellous [Lord]</l>
<l rend="indent">who measured the worlds turning into a dwarf.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
